Monitor disk usage of all your ec2 instances
================================================

Gets the disk usage stats(df) of all your instances and sends an email to the
specified email addresses. You can also add filters to get notifications when disk usage of a partition crosses a
predefined value.

Run:
bundle install

Usage:
ec2 = EC2Helpers.new(70, ec2 access key, ec2 secret key, "example@ex.com")
ec2.get_disk_info_of(ec2.app_servers)
